com.bigdata.bop.join

Class JVMDistinctFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bigdata.bop.join.JVMDistinctFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDistinctFilter

    public class JVMDistinctFilter
extends Object
implements IDistinctFilter
    Utility class for imposing a DISTINCT filter on IBindingSet. This class is thread-safe. It is based on a ConcurrentHashMap.
    Author:
    Bryan Thompson
